      "utilityType": "other",
      "description": "For up to 1 hour with concentration, the caster becomes Invisible while an illusory double appears in the caster space; the double lasts for the duration, the invisibility ends if the caster attacks or casts a spell, the caster can use a Magic action to move the double up to twice Speed and make it gesture, speak, or behave, and can use a Bonus Action each turn to switch between the double senses and their own, becoming Blinded and Deafened to their own surroundings while using the double senses.",
